    "en": {
      "title": "100 million donation from Dhammika Perera",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Investment Promotion Minister Dhammika Perera said that new immigration department offices will be opened in five cities including Batticaloa, Jaffna, Nuwara Eliya and Ratnapura.",
        "He said that there is a stock of necessary equipment for these five offices and he will donate 100 million rupees from his personal money for the rest of the work.",
        "He also said that the one-day service will also be started from Kurunegala from next Monday."
      ],
